title: Add the location -1,-135 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0x716954738e57686a08902d9dd586e813490fee23 (HirotoKai)

## Double Road - Double Corner

![Double Road - Double Corner](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/-1/-135/map.png)

Should the scene located at -1,-135 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

Hiroto Kai's - Glass Temple is a place where Music, Art, and People have a home! The beautiful architecture shows off the realistic Stain Glass Windows and Wooden construction. Hiroto Kai's Art/Wearables are showcased along the walls of the Gallery.

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=c9674f10-e574-11eb-bb4e-e9e2ebbd7fce)**
